This folder contains local Excel result files.
One file per module — mirrors the Google Sheet structure exactly.

Structure per file:
Columns: Test Case ID | Test Case Description | Steps | Expected Result | Actual Result | Comments | [Run Date-Time columns...]

Files:
- LOGIN_Results.xlsx
- TICKETS_Results.xlsx
- USERS_Results.xlsx
- RBAC_Results.xlsx
- MASTERDATA_Results.xlsx
- SLA_Results.xlsx
- KNOWLEDGEBASE_Results.xlsx
- PROJECTS_Results.xlsx
